                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="1-what-is-the-passage-about2-when-did-the-battle-take-place3-where-did-it-happen4-what-caused-the-battle5-what-do-think-about-the-indonesian-military-power-compared-to-that-of-the-british">
                            29. 1. What is the passage about?
